article.description: — Manny Camper had 19 points and 13 rebounds to carry Siena to a 63-50 win over Marist on Sunday.
article.headline: Camper lifts Siena over Marist 63-50
article.story: POUGHKEEPSIE, N.Y. -- — Manny Camper had 19 points and 13 rebounds to carry Siena to a 63-50 win over Marist on Sunday. Jalen Pickett had 11 points for Siena (8-2, 8-2 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Jackson Stormo added five assists. Marist totaled 23 points in the second half, a season low for the team. Hakim Bird and Richardo Wright had nine points each for the Red Foxes (9-7, 7-7). Marist defeated Siena 55-54 on Saturday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
